  "instructions": [
    "In a large pot, mix the flour with water to create a slurry.",
    "Add the onion slices to the pot and cook over medium heat for about 20 minutes until softened.",
    "Stir in garlic, lemon juice, soy sauce, cumin, smoked paprika, salt, and pepper. Bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for an additional 15-20 minutes or until the stew thickens slightly.",
    "Serve hot with gluten-free bread."
